==评价==
Surface Studio 得到了部分技术评论家的好评，他们称赞这种大型高分辨率显示器，《[[Verge|Verge]]》的汤姆·沃伦称其为“我用过的最好的桌面显示器之一”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/11/17/13663112/microsoft-surface-studio-review |title=Microsoft Surface Studio review: a beautiful invader of Apple's base |last=Warren |first=Tom |website=The Verge |date=Nov 17, 2016 |access-date=April 21, 2017 |archive-date=2020-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523150008/https://www.theverge.com/2016/11/17/13663112/microsoft-surface-studio-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>评论家也赞扬 Surface Studio 的外形设计和质量较好。对其的批评则包括价格昂贵、所有后置 I/O 端口，以及配置的不是最新一代的英特尔 CPU 和 Nvidia GPU。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.techradar.com/reviews/surface-studio |title=Microsoft Surface Studio review |last=Lee |first=Kevin |website=TechRadar |access-date=April 21, 2017 |archive-date=2020-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200311041435/https://www.techradar.com/reviews/surface-studio |dead-url=no }}</ref>

